CarrierDetails.Name: National General
CarrierDetails.DisclaimerHtml:
National General

The following applies to any plans sold with Association:
L.I.F.E. Membership privileges include life-style related benefits and services in programs offered by the Association. By applying for membership, you understand that dues are required and if participating in a sponsored insurance program, your Association membership annual dues may be collected in installments along with your insurance premiums. Membership in an Association may be required in order to be eligible for this insurance coverage.

Upon purchase, Premium Adjustments could be made to the Total Premium to remove duplicate membership costs.Â  Only one membership is required for all National General Accident & Health products being purchased.
